===Etymology===
Borrowed into late {{inh|en|enm|-}} from {{der|en|LL.|īnscrūtābilis}}, from {{m|la|in-||not}} + {{m|la|scrūtō||to examine}}, corresponding to {{prefix|en|in|scrutable}}

